«In Loving Memory of
Ronald Willis
(Ron)
1937 - 2019
Please sit awhile and enjoy
this beautiful place,
where I used to fish as a boy
and in later years.
So to all those that think of me,
we will miss each other for a while
and if others wonder why I'm missin
just tell em' I've sens fishin"´
±In memory of
David Stanley Howard
1971 - 2021
Devoted family man, music lover, raconteur and friend
"Captured my heart, captured my memory, captured a time for me,
I could see a time for me was gonna be, deep in my heart, deep in my memory"
Remembered with Love and a smile. We miss you always Dave.␀ذپ"	Sى)␀’ç"	‏’␀›ç"	شخ␀␀)%ذµ"	œھ␀ھç"	خ–␀ °ç"	کِ␀
